These project of smale program is about sale exihibition
How these project of smale program will operate
The users who will apply these smale program he or she wil get message immediately
about price and names of product, then after user wil abtain area to fillquantity
of product user has purchased therefore program will determine totol and average
according to price, after that program will display that if average price is above
15000 program will indicate that price is above or below 15000 then program will 
determine maximum, minimum, totol and average.
